rows.label: qst200801_msg0001
rows.name:
Hey, everyone! Look at that
Saffronia tree! Isn't it gorgeous?

rows.label: qst200801_msg0002
rows.name: Well, I think so, at least...

rows.label: qst200801_msg0008
rows.name:
The what? Me? Huh? I
don't understand...

rows.label: qst200801_msg0010
rows.name:
We know you have them!
Our intel is ironclad!

rows.label: qst200801_msg0011
rows.name:
You can very well say that, but I
still have no idea what you mean...

rows.label: qst200801_msg0012
rows.name:
Hotaru, are you sure you
don't know anything?

rows.label: qst200801_msg0014
rows.name:
Well, that's that then.
Maybe you're just confused?

rows.label: qst200801_msg0015
rows.name:
Hah! If that's how you
wanna play this...

rows.label: qst200801_msg0016
rows.name: I'm gonna make you return them!

rows.label: qst200801_msg0017
rows.name:
Oh dear, I hate it when
people get savage...

rows.label: qst200801_msg0018
rows.name:
Shut your mouth! You've
brought it on yourselves!

rows.label: qst200801_msg0019
rows.name: You can't talk your way outta this!
